y(已纳入 web/xlsx/manual 候选解析)\n- 实查:account_holdings_selected_latest.csv 已生成,23行;selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json 已生成;generate_actionable_brief / generate_daily_exec_card / check_stop_loss 均可读 selected 主源\n- 2026-04-01 06:41 生成盘级 runtime truth:research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest_{aggressive,balanced,defensive}.json;状态分别为 aggressive=normal/buy_authorized=true,balanced=risk_off/buy_authorized=true,defensive=BUY_HALT/buy_authorized=false。\n- 2026-04-01 06:46 重跑三盘 probe_guard + guard 总表:research/reports/strategy_probe_guard_summary_20260330.md,验证不再三盘同封。\n- 2026-04-01 06:41 aggressive orders 已重跑:research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv。\n- 2026-04-01 06:57 balanced 复跑完成:research/reports/paper_balanced_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv;overlay=research/reports/paper_balanced_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json,cached_count=13,missing_count=0。\n- 2026-04-01 07:00 defensive 复跑完成:research/reports/paper_defensive_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv;overlay=research/reports/paper_defensive_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json,cached_count=13,missing_count=0。\n- 2026-04-01 07:24-07:29 已落地分层配置:config/strategy_smallcap_chip_balanced.yaml、config/strategy_smallcap_chip_defensive.yaml,并更新 config/paper_live_trading_aggressive_v1.json、config/live_trading_exit_candidate_dual_v1.json、config/live_trading_exit_candidate_tight_v1.json。\n- 2026-04-01 07:28 生成配置分层报告:quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/t05_profile_config_split_20260330.md。\n- 2026-04-01 07:26 候选源烟雾验证阻断:generate_live_smallcap_candidates.py 回放 20260330 时 daily_basic_trade_date=20260309,basic lag=21 天;阻断属于本地数据源过旧,不是 Tavily。\n- 2026-04-01 08:02-08:10 alpha55 单列修复首轮落地:修复 scripts/run_qlib_alpha55_live_signal.py(总权重改为 regime_scale、增加 stale guard)与 scripts/run_alpha55_paper_sim.py(跳过过期 Alpha158,优先同日 RD);报告=quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/alpha55_weight_output_fix_progress_20260401.md。\n- 2026-04-01 08:06 烟雾验证:旧样本 alpha55_alpha1