out whether I should use my skills for any tasks.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_UKmodatHGDhV2Xo0NKgNmE05|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bd481969288628b73ab69df","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aepcKc1scclVHzWDMr04LMYI|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bec81968dc2e0309176b227","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f6aaVkyeEf88XCfPsTSQetTo|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bf48196a7d4aa7cdcb4238a","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":31839,"output":630,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32469,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775073733765,"responseId":"resp_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79c6a5f8819694586403a81e9ca1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"feb9f885","parentId":"7c219ce5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:02:34.068Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_UKmodatHGDhV2Xo0NKgNmE05|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bd481969288628b73ab69df","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775073754062}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0f008b4","parentId":"feb9f885","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:02:34.074Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_aepcKc1scclVHzWDMr04LMYI|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bec81968dc2e0309176b227","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775073754068}}
{"type":"message","id":"d735eb8b","parentId":"a0f008b4","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:02:34.079Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f6aaVkyeEf88XCfPsTSQetTo|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79d97bf48196a7d4aa7cdcb4238a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775073754074}}
{"type":"message","id":"8552fa88","parentId":"d735eb8b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:03:04.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering task execution**\n\nIt looks like I need to check due tasks. The workspace backup should be checked daily, and since it’s 4:01 AM, it seems like now is a good time for that. I’m thinking the quant operations can wait until later today at 09:20. Also, even though the user heartbeat indicates everything is okay, I’ll reply with HEARTBEAT_OK. I might want to run checks quietly and only alert if there are issues; that feels appropriate.\n\n**Evaluating task response**\n\nI'm considering if tasks generate new files that need reporting. The user wants me to reply with HEARTBEAT_OK if everything's fine. If there's something that needs attention, I should report that. I'm thinking about running a git status check in the workspace directory, but I need to be careful about making destructive changes. Since pushing requires external action and might need user authorization, it's perhaps best to just check the status and only alert if there are pending items.\n\n**Considering task execution**\n\nI'm deliberating on whether uncommitted changes indicate something I need to note. If nothing is urgent, it might be fine to keep things quiet. I think I should run the quant mainline health script since it's an internal task that's allowed. I also want to check the workspace's git status. While I could look at the morning push state file, since it's 4:01 AM, that seems unnecessary right now. The daily audit, enhancement, and dashboard checks do need to be executed once a day.\n\n**Running lightweight commands**\n\nI’m thinking of running some lightweight commands like checking the git status using `git status --porcelain` within the `/.openclaw` directory to see if there are changes, although I can’t push. It’s likely a manageable task, and I might also want to check the morning state file. I’ll need to ensure that running these commands together with exec is feasible without causing a rapid loop. Using a timeout of 300 could help with that setup. Let’s proceed!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79e265848196a9babefb277e0700\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzXn3jPOkc0Hd1b3p7zMraNzyJa3mAV78mkVrjISl7JJvMjtE9OJtZYzoLzxlKkRoLc8HTiVd2LygonNoIDXqQb5V3FqZEkkC9ESpvpxTBFmL6mQJldDxkk97KwvYNWS2Gii3xcpDWhhBpWV6RGByKDPkYinIROPuG1-iY7lcuBzRAgkwFjwfhXGqOBlDcduNmBL_QENIQ9AYFcDcx_vzeaGib1Re6O-6VobeZnp56uOaJ8IO0u72hgeJqMykrT10JJ5OYnSZBVH0FcLGF4W2mozf0Sn59n97oZPgKnK5uzYWwSIsMPvIL4opcOErCqby7JIdW3X8kaNh0BduHTGO76sgNDq_flzGEtYwKaN0iLM8Xx0cXd3G1JYsIEJuoyu-6tKbu3_aURwhRvHcEQ9IBKIjukPlD0zb9wmh0VCQuCjgHHv3HBaj-0tF-8vgKzF2ANbUO9_eEgUQ88Fm1Un2_qU5o0ZbOMiv4l6ly-qnQWzJPFzcinAkCZNVhyV6yYwbUpxr_lIAWjMboDp8U3gB_6lpsmdkHhdCEMIO8-IjGVlQqvoy7u7zX5opdlUJvu12LkEYRz0doxovLr4huyAGCEMGExjRdJdIt63trxnhChgCAb_FR3Q-KRGqPH4sebaYePqe5GNE7JEq0-DsJj4r4YspMnTUYPUAPAe8r8j4iDnJJOSiv2902ixgib0HQ3CjY1wgI8lE2MNle7-Pk3RYhGBW4tO5Oj9CzbVADwb3uXsoZ6rkmD4BEWDQjWoKGM76_68fR694zCyvgB3WHcq5sHCJdWJmNmfgEYbmcUk8oVDc5NWl6T0WWw5HadKQNr4NcGZa_vWpP3AqTcud88Vl_Ywmj5GjU2cFxlWhB6-VZstF0p7JlNgjl1fUkQMeWngP6YhpmRGmBIIhqTeLrohWxL44MMRa35o_CrHwNOTDVdn8gYyaDn1aAG2Gn6n3QdBm9k5g8ZFp2oyyAaDRxa10A0z5M1FPjfwcIZBW8PIvtHetY06V43c_Qk2MpX4QXNYKAHXgO-1qFjQkBg4jdiCoYoTuiTXP5xLq0d8wd_7FKO8l0cjmE65zwpY_VHWCIdR1L3uT6gBLO33XoGd5lAx7TsvUMRDQNIIGzQBwb1X2DnBbF_ZUm22aCN4NY8s9GfSy6BDS2-dCI1qFV1lLYTJIlwaC1gS1wowaOi38CpXoCai7yXzj-tSDM0Kv7Hc8wDVJ64En8TA8vOFdyBq15KOl8-5G_E2PpJ0Hyt8rB2chYpXrpadGazTQgkQB1rXkioz7PP3NQQjmG1T_GVSCLtxKsMKr39z6MTStRB80dTaAH9pc4ewWcf3DwuLE1X_9oxrEanw91IWPwzV1vkHa0Dds2GPv-vIjOEpccn_AWvm9hoyvUL0yVWqhb9-BCzsMtlN-dC7MFigoY9hvW4KRRBoAPCxMvqrVMgFoaYl1htshUEOiMEvlJ1UtvpfSmBUQlvGc6tC9vwFqv8gdj5xjIsEbkvHIfhfYx0lIxGjNLJ1handl-prj10UgwQJw1wAmMFPhPGvw7lm4gETEbQCGo38qRMPUorz7czIQrfFRt5XWWLEZ1-HrFJLUmoj7co2g7N1v1Z9rRSp3yNBB5dozlTkPRwsF_AHuOFS6gYZ5lbHJ1lqH8OCjWJKkZf7x-BYLxrZB5pyS8MUz_MBVC3vxHH3by28WdXKhGbXN5JF