 > 景气成长 > 轮动低吸 > 防守\\n- 开盘触发条件：若开盘放量上攻，可跟主线强势板块；若冲高回落，及时收回到高股息和防御。\\n- 先看主线：中东冲突延续，金油避险交易升温\\n- 再看压制项：美元与美债利率维持偏强\\n- 最后看环境项：隔夜全球股市普遍回落\\n- 优先关注：黄金、军工、能源、高股息\\n- 尽量回避：成长科技、高估值题材、出口链、航空\\n- 详细版已落地到 workspace 报告目录。\",\n  \"deadline\": \"08:51\",\n  \"deadline_checked_at\": \"2026-03-30 08:51:01\",\n  \"deadline_alerted_date\": \"2026-03-30\",\n  \"deadline_alert\": {\n    \"ok\": false,\n    \"info\": \"env: node: No such file or directory\",\n    \"dry_run\": false\n  },\n  \"last_push_at\": \"2026-03-30 20:03:00\",\n  \"push_note\": \"Cron push failed (LiveSessionModelSwitchError); manually recovered and pushed via message tool\"\n}\n=== MAINLINE_GUARD ===\n🚨 量化投研主链巡检：告警\n- 08:50晨报：`MISSING` | 最近成功：`None`\n- 晨报状态说明：`缺少晨报状态文件。`\n- 稳定策略：`-` | 年化/回撤/夏普：`None` / `None` / `None`\n- 回测队列：`-` | 运行中：`None` | 已纳入稳定策略：`-`\n- 模拟盘快照：`None` | 新鲜度：`-` | 说明：`None`\n- 缺口：08:50晨报链路正常, 稳定策略审计正常, 回测队列正常, 发布汇总快照正常, 首席面板已生成, 首席播报已生成, 总控台卡片已生成, 模拟盘快照为今日口径\n- 健康报告：`暂无`\n- 处理建议：优先检查晨报、稳定策略审计、回测队列三项是否断裂，再决定是否暂停后续自动发布。\n- 健康报告：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_20260402.md`\n- 健康JSON：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_20260402.json`\n\n(Command exited with code 20)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775073785973}}
{"type":"message","id":"62a33c15","parentId":"99a7d596","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:03:19.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating health reports**\n\nI found an alert from the mainline guard that seems inconsistent with the situation this morning. It looks like it might have the wrong date because there's an 08:50 report marked as missing. But it’s also saying the link is normal, which feels contradictory. I need to check if this truly warrants an alert according to the rules. Timing might be a factor since it’s before 08:50. I should read the health report JSON to verify everything.\n\n**Analyzing alert reasoning**\n\nI need to check if the alert is only due to the morning report being missing. Since it’s before 08:50, it probably shouldn’t count as a valid alert. Maybe the heartbeats shouldn't refer to old tasks, but they could indicate a misconfigured false alert. The user just asked if anything needs attention, and although the script indicates an alert, it seems like a false positive. At 4:01, a missing morning report isn't actionable, so I’ll inspect the JSON for clarity.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_04474edf112ffe0c0169cd79fd998c8196ac1f9ec7f5a07754\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzXoHpB3Uqdx4kpBwfzVawR7PQ6_jTEvXB7uOGajgOTb9wllJwLmWcFp1GqoHRCkP0bhyJIO2fT6lSqFhYtaHl2a4XQ3uQcIAnDr4LUtE0uDD6MlFm5fcVo6R2kiVBB5lKgpYqxUVXmZ15O3DUTc5nPs2YSJqZZUFmxVobmOehj_v_ZoJMoQAcs0C6WmP__y0PWU0-xi4TPiR6HiO9IWYoutdFRURYSFlUs4JK5ZabiYCm1qlSLIYZUFGiS0qtLwJ-NUC5EVuI9GmX6PlAxwzlEehSBiyL9t1wkOrGTxfQuRIKJ-wFSmRP7fhN3Ghvrm9Gluz839P-UCFqg6qPlhxaCPwu68VhcbUaHHJWdqiuhr9D4viX6aBYDVekZASHQAnf9Mr-f79QsC0kWFDL0lPTiz4pQimlb3QI5e2Tb4tcne5e7W3VZIknixro_ReXk9b3Z5f0jEUkUPhx0rtiCer0g6WOkd1o7xlj4dSarLIEwocXPhOvyFJ_Ebuzp6cGuxkB7Qm_I2QsS-HDqAUysKEKwHW7eAZ-Hqx2qeR_4hPf7LqY3lhy7cPst44K4ddk_yTqc_UbZi6QOMFaGLVDbS0ZDh0DRwpR6A60GoM-vXmykMTlk-1aMZ8RLb9dTIFOO4CYr6ZUt3c8j_2Nm09bLQHhzrnPpSYHJgm3uDGiiNAnOVKpUaAx3I49IFVDb8OnnwJ6DIBIDOW