{"type":"message","id":"b65c2041","parentId":"41db0074","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:09:34.975Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dEvlpVB25OinEssHEXbJjZgs|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cda5ae718481969e8a2026afdce6ec","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775084974965}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a9984d7","parentId":"b65c2041","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:09:34.981Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sGOXTCuLCAdNewh6kSNewa6r|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cda5ae71908196ac86848f7c0d26aa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-04-02 07:04\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 07:05\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲明确指令“你开个子代理继续修复”\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260401.md\n\n## Goal\n- 连续推进模拟盘主链修复收口：解决三盘 `dated_artifact_tag_mismatch` / `paper_profile_common_date_missing`，统一审计/控制塔/账户口径，并给出盘前可验收结果\n\n## Acceptance\n- `daily_strategy_audit_latest.*` 不再把 aggressive / balanced / defensive 标为 `dated_artifact_tag_mismatch`\n- 三盘公共日期与账户/审计/控制塔口径一致，`paper_profile_common_date_missing` 消失或被明确替换为真实阻断原因\n- 输出一份新的修复结果文件，明确说明三盘当前状态、剩余阻断与是否影响盘前运行\n\n## Current\n- 等待子代理完成修复并核对子代理回传的新增产物、报告路径与 commit hash\n\n## Next\n- 如子代理已达验收，整理盘前可验收结论并回传张玲\n- 如仍有阻断，提炼剩余根因、影响范围与下一最小修复件\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 07:04] 已将主任务切回模拟盘修复收口，暂停此前被插单的其他旁支任务\n- 启动子代理执行模拟盘修复收口，并要求其直接修改代码/配置/报表链路后回传验收件\n- [2026-04-02 07:05] 已启动隔离子代理继续修复模拟盘主链；runId=3f561fb1-4c1b-4484-84c9-3f7762db51a6，childSessionKey=agent:main:subagent:3646e638-d66e-45e2-9dcb-b5ebf8f0813e\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260401.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy_probe_guard_summary_20260401.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/control_tower_daily_latest.json\n- sessions_spawn runId=3f561fb1-4c1b-4484-84c9-3f7762db51a6 childSessionKey=agent:main:subagent:3646e638-d66e-45e2-9dcb-b5ebf8f0813e label=paper-trading-repair-20260402-0705\n\n## Blockers\n- 当前仅完成首轮分层与补跑，审计口径仍有 `dat