name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list","recentMinutes":90},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"list\",\"recentMinutes\":90}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":433,"output":476,"cacheRead":91648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775088661152,"responseId":"resp_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdb435bc6c8196b7488c1310d12beb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e8a152b","parentId":"b56b7cce","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:11:43.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fUdCkvvUUBbaup1dE9L2PTJc|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdb43f78dc8196b0c5d4d28c4bf90e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775088703910}}
{"type":"message","id":"327df16a","parentId":"8e8a152b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:11:43.921Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0vpBLCTPaKP4tE48BPec9qCZ|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdb43f78ec8196b05c539a7c1104d4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-04-02 07:31\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 07:56\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲明确指令“你把全量的仓库都加入扫描的名单，每天报告是否有更新”\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json\n\n## Goal\n- 将 workspace 内全量 Git 仓库纳入 github-repo-monitor 扫描名单，并确保每天自动产出更新报告\n\n## Acceptance\n- `config/repos.json` 已扩为全量仓库名单\n- 自动调度存在且可用\n- 完成一次配置加载/首轮手动触发验收，确认脚本按新清单运行\n\n## Current\n- 保持主任务 active：execution_layer journal_missing 仍待修复；下一步需直接定位 run_close_review_v2 / generate_control_tower_daily 的最新文件选择与 journal 计数逻辑\n\n## Next\n- 产出 execution_journal_missing_repair_20260402 或 execution_journal_missing_blocker_20260402 报告并提交 commit\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 07:29] 已扫描 workspace 下可识别的 Git 仓库，并去掉嵌套重复仓（如 `SideLinker-Home/docs`）\n- [2026-04-02 07:29] 已确认 `com.ling.github-repo-monitor` LaunchAgent 存在且已加载\n- [2026-04-02 07:29] 已确认 LaunchAgent 当前为每日 09:00 自动执行\n- [2026-04-02 07:31] 已将 22 个仓库写入 `~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json`\n- [2026-04-02 07:39] 上一子代理未交付 journal_missing 修复验收件；仅确认本机缺少 pytest，改用 unittest，不构成主任务新增验收产物\n- 补全 github-repo-monitor 清单到实际监控仓库，并跑通一次手动触发验收留痕\n- [2026-04-02 07:55] 第二轮子代理仅完成最小回归说明，未产出 execution_journal_missing 修复/阻断报告；control_tower 仍为 FULL_HALT: journal_missing，不计为验收完成\n\n## Evidence\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json`\n- `/Users/ling/Library/LaunchAgents/com.ling.github-repo-monitor.plist`\n- `launchctl list | grep github-repo-monitor`\n- 核查结果：control_tower_daily_latest.json 仍为 execution_layer.FULL_HALT / journal_missing；git log 最新仍是 17379d1fa\n- [2026-04-02 07:43] 已修复 ACTIVE_TASK 漂移：移除与 Goal 不一致的 FULL_HALT/journal_missing 执行项\n- [2026