g a daily audit to ensure everything is functioning smoothly.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Checking task status**\\n\\nI need to check the ACTIVE_TASK status because every heartbeat executes certain conditions. If the status is active and there's content in Next, I should decide whether to spawn or yield. I want to inspect the current ACTIVE_TASK to see if it is completed. I’ll read the HEARTBEAT and ACTIVE_TASK, and also check the status files for any updates. It might be good to run parallel reads on the morning state and enhancement files. If nothing has changed, I’ll simply respond with HEARTBEAT_OK.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"先做一轮轻量核查：HEARTBEAT、ACTIVE_TASK、晨报状态、盘前强检和日审计是否有新变化。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf095f7ac819698db3a58fb02c5e9\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_SvIwtbpBHToPM4AL1HzphSTE|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f0c819681f2e95322952f2b","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_U3etEvfFhGsfn9x4bldNWgJ3|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f1c8196889415facc517535","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ltRrwgRbZ3eiEfudPYVJhRwt|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f2481968264b92fcfe8400b","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_PUcIAcMJ3deXCjQ4tYhWioDl|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f2c8196882515d08517cde8","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260402.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260402.json\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ffvIQ3aqtyiolgXdYOF2eyu7|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f34819686092246b7ab6c10","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260402.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260402.json\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_UwW5BzmBGeyO4DZZqEUWACNu|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f3c8196a17caa6836582bd3","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260402.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260402.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":103241,"output":808,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104132942,"responseId":"resp_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf086642081968abea042950071bc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"78a846bc","parentId":"f5870a4a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:29:12.756Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_SvIwtbpBHToPM4AL1HzphSTE|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169cdf0982f0c819681f2e95322952f2b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104152752}}
