✅ Sent via Feishu. Message ID: om_x100b53f2f37d7cb8c4dc88e5c9824c6\"\n  },\n  \"brief_message\": \"🌅 晨会摘要｜2026-04-01\\n- 盘前一句话：盘前情绪不差，可以先看进攻方向，但依旧别无脑追高。\\n- 全球风险偏好：偏多；A股体温：28/100（冰冷）；操作基调：偏进攻\\n- 盘前优先级：进攻主线 > 景气成长 > 轮动低吸 > 防守\\n- 开盘触发条件：若开盘放量上攻，可跟主线强势板块；若冲高回落，及时收回到高股息和防御。\\n- 先看主线：中东冲突延续，金油避险交易升温\\n- 再看压制项：美元与美债利率维持偏强\\n- 最后看环境项：隔夜全球股市普遍回落\\n- 优先关注：黄金、军工、能源、高股息\\n- 尽量回避：成长科技、高估值题材、出口链、航空\\n- 详细版已落地到 workspace 报告目录。\",\n  \"deadline\": \"08:51\",\n  \"deadline_checked_at\": \"2026-04-02 08:51:01\",\n  \"deadline_alerted_date\": \"2026-04-02\",\n  \"deadline_alert\": {\n    \"ok\": false,\n    \"info\": \"env: node: No such file or directory\",\n    \"dry_run\": false\n  },\n  \"last_push_at\": \"2026-03-30 20:03:00\",\n  \"push_note\": \"Cron push failed (LiveSessionModelSwitchError); manually recovered and pushed via message tool\",\n  \"stdout\": \"\",\n  \"stderr\": \".14/site-packages/yfinance/base.py\\\", line 135, in _lazy_load_price_history\\n    self._price_history = PriceHistory(self._data, self.ticker, self._get_ticker_tz(timeout=10))\\n                                                                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^\\n  File \\\"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/yfinance/base.py\\\", line 150, in _get_ticker_tz\\n    tz = self._fetch_ticker_tz(timeout)\\n  File \\\"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/yfinance/utils.py\\\", line 95, in wrapper\\n    result = func(*args, **kwargs)\\n  File \\\"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/yfinance/base.py\\\", line 182, in _fetch_ticker_tz\\n    data = self._data.cache_get(url=url, params=params, timeout=timeout)\\n  File \\\"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/yfinance/data.py\\\", line 46, in wrapped\\n    return func(*args, **kwargs)\\n  File \\\"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/y