{"type":"message","id":"6f57d8ab","parentId":"465981cb","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:57:41.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same routine. Read HEARTBEAT and ACTIVE_TASK, do the scheduled checks, reply HEARTBEAT_OK if nothing needs attention.","thinkingSignature":"8ba91aa395e130a7e23c6ca53adbeed26f1f1501417f4848759ef4068c2fe591"},{"type":"text","text":"收到。先读 HEARTBEAT 与 ACTIVE_TASK，再对今日量化和主动汇报事项做一轮下午快查。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ijai38o5uph_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ijai38o5uph_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ijai38o5uph_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\npython3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport json, glob\n\nbase = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace')\nquant = base/'quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system'\n\n# 1. morning state\nmstate = base/'memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json'\nmorning = json.loads(mstate.read_text()) if mstate.exists() else {}\nm_status = morning.get('status', 'N/A')\nm_success = morning.get('last_success_at', 'N/A')\nm_is_today = morning.get('date') == '2026-04-02'\n\n# 2. precheck\npre = sorted((quant/'research/reports').glob('auto_premarket_precheck_20260402*'))\npre_data = json.loads(pre[-1].read_text()) if pre else {}\npre_status = pre_data.get('status', 'N/A')\npre_reason = pre_data.get('status_reason', pre_data.get('halt_reason','N/A'))\n\n# 3. audit\naudit = sorted((quant/'research/reports').glob('daily_strategy_audit_20260402*'))\naudit_data = json.loads(audit[-1].read_text()) if audit else {}\naudit_status = audit_data.get('overall_status', 'N/A')\naudit_precheck = audit_data.get('precheck_status', 'N/A')\n\n# 4. enhancement\nenh = sorted((quant/'research/reports').glob('daily_enhancement_20260402*'))\nenh_data = json.loads(enh[-1].read_text()) if enh else {}\nenh_status = enh_data.get('dual_source', {}).get('status', 'N/A')\nenh_heatmap = enh_data.get('heatmap', {}).get('status', 'N/A')\nenh_summary = enh_data.get('dual_source', {}).get('summary', '')\n\n# 5. control tower\nct = sorted((quant/'research/reports').glob('control_tower_daily_latest.json'))\nct_data = json.loads(ct[-1].read_text()) if ct else {}\nct_exec = ct_data.get('execution_layer', {})\nct_trading = ct_exec.get('trading_status', 'N/A')\nct_reason = ct_exec.get('reason', 'N/A')\n\nprint(json.dumps({\n    'morning': {'status': m_status, 'is_today': m_is_today, 'last_success': m_success},\n    'precheck': {'status': pre_status, 'reason': pre_reason},\n    'audit': {'overall': audit_status, 'precheck': audit_precheck},\n    'enhancement': {'dual_source': enh_status, 'heatmap': enh_heatmap},\n    'control_tower': {'trading_status': ct_trading, 'reason': ct_reason}\n}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":60,"yieldMs":8000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":782,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":118929,"totalTokens":119785,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775120234202,"responseId":"061d626ae7411b3b9f91efcad7e8eb6a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3681b7f5","parentId":"6f57d8ab","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:57:41.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0ijai38o5uph_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775120261682}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a154b58","parentId":"3681b7f5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:57:41.702Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0ijai38o5uph_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ACTIVE_TASK.md - 量化策略增强：市场过滤器 + 多指标共振\n\n## 目标\n在现有 Qlib breadth + turnover 策略基础上嫁接两个增强模块：\n1. **市场环境过滤器**：波动率收缩 / ADX / BB带宽三重过滤\n2. **多指标共振信号**：用 breadth + 动量 + 趋势强度构建复合信号\n\n## 验收件\n- `breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json` 更新，新口径含过滤器版本\n- `breadth_strict_oos_dashboard_latest.html` 更新，新面板含共振信号展示\n- 回测报告：新口径 vs 旧口径对比（年化 / 夏普 / 最大回撤）\n- git commit\n\n## 执行记录\n### [2026-04-02 16:34] 张玲确认执行：两个方向全部采纳\n\n## 当前状态\n- Status: active\n- Started: 2026-04-02 16:34\n- Updated: 2026-04-02 16:34\n- Blockers: 暂无\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 找到现有策略代码位置\n2. 添加市场环境过滤器模块（BB带宽 / ADX / 波动率门槛）\n3. 添加多指标共振信号模块（breadth + 动量 + 趋势强度）\n4. 运行回测对比新旧口径\n5. 更新 dashboard 展示新信号\n6. Git commit\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 16:34] 张玲确认执行方向一（市场环境过滤器）和方向二（多指标共振）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775120261692}}
