{"type":"message","id":"0b775711","parentId":"48297286","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:58:08.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The exec had a JSON decode error on reading precheck. Let me fix and re-read. The precheck file exists, so the issue is probably empty/corrupt file. Let me just use a simpler approach without errors. Also, the ACTIVE_TASK shows it's active with a new task: market filter + multi-indicator resonance strategy enhancement.Let me also note: it's 16:57 now, so the market should be closed. The quant ops for the day include precheck (already done at 09:20), audit (already done), enhancements (already done at 12:29), and live dashboard (should check if done).For the heartbeat, the ACTIVE_TASK is active with Next items - so I need to either spawn a subagent or yield. Since it's a complex coding task (market filter + resonance signals), I should spawn a subagent to continue execution without waiting.Actually, the exec failed with JSON error. Let me just do a simpler check without the JSON parsing, then handle the ACTIVE_TASK.","thinkingSignature":"5ab4ad58deea1ead1bc31da7730713b6e5e500b60e12b2a38598218a558ad440"},{"type":"text","text":"\nACTIVE_TASK 是 active，内容是新的量化策略增强任务（市场过滤器 + 多指标共振）。这是张玲刚确认的方向，需要立即推进。同时 exec 报错了，我换方式快速核查关键状态。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lgcp79lacr75_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\nBASE=/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nQUANT=$BASE/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\n\n# morning state - simple check\necho \"=== MORNING STATE ===\"\nif [ -s $BASE/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json ]; then\n  python3 -c \"import json; d=json.load(open('$BASE/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json')); print(f'status={d[\\\"status\\\"]} date={d.get(\\\"date\\\",\\\"?\\\")} last_success={d.get(\\\"last_success_at\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\"\nelse\n  echo \"MISSING\"\nfi\n\n# precheck - check if today's file exists and has content\necho \"=== PRECHECK ===\"\nPRECHECK=$QUANT/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260402.json\nif [ -s \"$PRECHECK\" ]; then\n  python3 -c \"import json; d=json.load(open('$PRECHECK')); print(f'status={d.get(\\\"status\\\",\\\"?\\\")} reason={d.get(\\\"status_reason\\\",d.get(\\\"halt_reason\\\",\\\"?\\\"))}')\"\nelse\n  echo \"MISSING\"\nfi\n\n# control tower latest\necho \"=== CONTROL TOWER ===\"\nCT=$QUANT/research/reports/control_tower_daily_latest.json\nif [ -s \"$CT\" ]; then\n  python3 -c \"import json; d=json.load(open('$CT')); el=d.get('execution_layer',{}); print(f'trading_status={el.get(\\\"trading_status\\\",\\\"?\\\")} reason={el.get(\\\"reason\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\"\nelse\n  echo \"MISSING\"\nfi\n\n# audit\necho \"=== AUDIT ===\"\nAUDIT=$QUANT/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260402.json\nif [ -s \"$AUDIT\" ]; then\n  python3 -c \"import json; d=json.load(open('$AUDIT')); print(f'overall={d.get(\\\"overall_status\\\",\\\"?\\\")} precheck={d.get(\\\"precheck_status\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\"\nelse\n  echo \"MISSING\"\nfi","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30,"yieldMs":8000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95519,"output":789,"cacheRead":25427,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775120261737,"responseId":"061d6285d8ca273a42ac390689104902"}}
