{"type":"message","id":"f98a60c4","parentId":"ffa6faa9","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:00:33.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Heartbeat at 9:00 PM. I need to read HEARTBEAT and check ACTIVE_TASK. The current time is 21:00, so it's within the \"quiet hours\" range (23:00-08:00 would be quiet, but 21:00 is not quiet hours). Wait, 23:00-08:00 is the quiet period. 21:00 is not in that range, so it's normal hours.\n\nACTIVE_TASK is active. I should check if there's been any subagent completion. I need to check if the subagent spawned earlier (at 16:57) has completed and delivered results. Since I yielded and am waiting for completion events, let me check.\n\n\nI'll read the HEARTBEAT and ACTIVE_TASK files to get the current status, and also check what subagents are currently running or if any have completed since my last check.","thinkingSignature":"fe3c26be644ee6785862c351375288676cafd90eeefa38d7494ea634af257892"},{"type":"text","text":"先读 HEARTBEAT 和 ACTIVE_TASK，再查子代理是否有新进展。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_90m7gaow6ygo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_90m7gaow6ygo_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_90m7gaow6ygo_3","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list","recentMinutes":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":124421,"totalTokens":124800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775134814366,"responseId":"061d9b5e2486498d44305d5293b72cf6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"536e4c2c","parentId":"f98a60c4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:00:33.091Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_90m7gaow6ygo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775134833081}}
{"type":"message","id":"dcbe3098","parentId":"536e4c2c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:00:33.104Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_90m7gaow6ygo_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ACTIVE_TASK.md - 归档\n## 状态: done\n## 归档时间: 2026-04-02 19:40\n## 目标: 量化策略增强：市场过滤器 + 多指标共振（已完成）\n\n## 产物路径\n- 增强模块: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_qlib_breadth_enhanced_filter.py`\n- 回测脚本: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_qlib_breadth_filter_backtest.py`\n- 回测报告: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/enhanced_filter_backtest_20260402_1835.json`\n- Dashboard: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/regime_overlay_ab_dashboard_latest.html`\n- Git commit: `7dc724c76`\n\n## 回测对比\n| 口径 | 年化 | 夏普 | 最大回撤 |\n|------|------|------|---------|\n| 旧口径 | 48.33% | 2.618 | 22.61% |\n| 新口径(估算) | 30.20% | 1.609 | 13.89% |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775134833091}}
