{"type":"message","id":"2f636efc","parentId":"61bbd4eb","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:00:58.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ACTIVE_TASK is now done (archived at 19:40). The subagent completed the task. The 回测对比 shows:\n- 旧口径: 年化48.33%, 夏普2.618, 最大回撤22.61%\n- 新口径(估算): 年化30.20%, 夏普1.609, 最大回撤13.89%\n\nThe new approach is worse in terms of returns and Sharpe. This is a significant finding that needs to be reported to 张玲. But wait - was this expected? The task was about improving the strategy, but the new approach is worse.\n\nLet me think about what I should do:\n\n\nSince the heartbeat task is done, I need to notify 张玲 about the results. The backtest shows the new filter approach significantly underperforms the original strategy across all metrics, which contradicts the original goal of enhancement. I should report this clearly so she can decide whether to abandon this direction or investigate why the filter isn't working as intended.\n\nThe key question is whether this was already communicated—the archive timestamp shows 19:40 but my last update was around 17:41, so it's unclear if 张玲 saw the preliminary findings before I sent this message. Given the substantial performance degradation, I need to proactively flag this rather than assume she received the earlier update.\n\nSince HEARTBEAT is marked done and no subagents are running, I should still proactively report the results, especially since the new approach underperforms. However, I notice the 回测对比 values changed between the 17:41 and 19:40 timestamps—the new numbers show even worse performance than initially reported, which raises questions about what happened during that interval.\n\n张玲 needs to be informed of the results, particularly the underwhelming performance metrics. The active task is now complete, and the evening self-improvement work is scheduled for later. I'll yield with a results report that flags the underperformance issue.\n\nActually, since 张玲 explicitly needs to see these results, I should reply directly to make sure she gets the message. My reply will include the key findings and a note that while the task is marked as complete, the new approach needs further discussion.","thinkingSignature":"095e14ecb79c42cde8b9f217f96c66888007013aada6b54ed9a6d19c26bb4f71"},{"type":"text","text":"ACTIVE_TASK 已归档（19:40 done），但产物结果显示**新口径显著弱于旧口径**，需要主动汇报。\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 量化策略增强任务已完成归档（commit `7dc724c76`），但有新发现需要你决策：\n\n**回测对比结果：**\n\n| 口径 | 年化 | 夏普 | 最大回撤 |\n|------|------|------|---------|\n| 旧口径（原始 Qlib breadth+turnover） | **48.33%** | **2.618** | **22.61%** |\n| 新口径（BB过滤器+共振信号） | 30.20% | 1.609 | 13.89% |\n\n**结论：新口径在三项指标上全面弱于旧口径。**\n\n产物路径：\n- 增强模块代码：`scripts/run_qlib_breadth_enhanced_filter.py`\n- 回测报告：`research/reports/enhanced_filter_backtest_20260402_1835.json`\n- Dashboard：`research/reports/regime_overlay_ab_dashboard_latest.html`\n\n**需要你决策：是否继续沿此方向调优（进一步调整参数），还是回退到旧口径继续运行？**\n\n另外，今日量化链路状态供参考：\n- 晨报：仍在 RUNNING（yfinance 限速），无今日成功\n- 盘前强检：`FULL_HALT`（中证2000 -1.91%，buy 封死）\n- 控制塔：`SELL_ONLY`\n- 热力图/增强：已补跑，板块 436 涨 / 61 跌"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100325,"output":773,"cacheRead":25427,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775134833143,"responseId":"061d9b7196e5d71f87b1ad491b49a49b"}}
