eeds my attention.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Executing self-improvement checks**\\n\\nIt's 22:17 in the evening, which means I should be running my self-improvement tasks now. I need to check if the output files for today exist; if they're missing, I might need to run those tasks. Even though it's within the quiet hours from 23:00 to 08:00, I can still perform checks now. I’ll read the HEARTBEAT and ACTIVE_TASK to determine what needs attention and decide whether to take action based on my schedule.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"先按 HEARTBEAT 做晚间检查：ACTIVE_TASK 状态、以及今日 self-improvement 是否已产出。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a84888081968dc764adca6a646a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kl0MRsUlIAXfB12k2judRs8q|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a872010819680fc4cb69db2b392","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6hnV4rB0DUMWtZbRlni8rBXE|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a8720248196a32433d65b29a500","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_VawYFucAK4NqeHXk6lGuAYg4|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a87202c8196a70cefeae049abbe","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nfor f in \\\n  memory/self_improvement_daily_20260402.md \\\n  memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260402.md \\\n  memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260402.md; do\n  if [ -f \"$f\" ]; then echo \"EXISTS $f\"; else echo \"MISSING $f\"; fi\ndone","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20,"yieldMs":5000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\\nfor f in \\\\\\n  memory/self_improvement_daily_20260402.md \\\\\\n  memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260402.md \\\\\\n  memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260402.md; do\\n  if [ -f \\\"$f\\\" ]; then echo \\\"EXISTS $f\\\"; else echo \\\"MISSING $f\\\"; fi\\ndone\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":20,\"yieldMs\":5000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":125790,"output":765,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126555,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775139426106,"responseId":"resp_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a66ad4c8196877fa5bd7d4cddc4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f8b3101","parentId":"217161c7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:17:44.327Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_kl0MRsUlIAXfB12k2judRs8q|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce7a872010819680fc4cb69db2b392","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775139464317}}
