nd flowing well, so let’s verify!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"先看 HEARTBEAT 和 ACTIVE_TASK 当前状态；如果联合回测已经落地，我只汇报新增产物。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce817294bc8196b47dfa54fa8ecbb3\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_muvau2ElKZkRrq4VD568FlIz|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce8172c5c08196b97f01c2e021005c","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7bMEzMq6FbqxxvZhzIf7KndC|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce8172c5d48196a66d6a3fd364cb6c","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":129075,"output":143,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129218,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775141226006,"responseId":"resp_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce816d4c488196be17237d873a9230"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db7d523b","parentId":"0971d550","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:47:16.046Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_muvau2ElKZkRrq4VD568FlIz|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce8172c5c08196b97f01c2e021005c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775141236037}}
{"type":"message","id":"149b9a2a","parentId":"db7d523b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:47:16.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7bMEzMq6FbqxxvZhzIf7KndC|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce8172c5d48196a66d6a3fd364cb6c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-02 22:30\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 22:42\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲确认继续执行双因子正式方案与稳健性验证\nResume Entry: 先看 ACTIVE_TASK.md，然后查看 dual_factor_formal_params.json 与 dual_factor_robustness_report.json\n\n## Goal\n- 基于已验证最优的 ROC10 + RSV5 双因子版本，产出正式可复用参数方案，并完成一轮更严格的稳健性验证\n\n## Acceptance\n- 生成正式参数方案文件（json 或 md），明确双因子参数与适用口径\n- 生成稳健性验证结果文件，至少覆盖不同时间窗或更保守参数的对比\n- 给出面向张玲的结论：是否建议进入下一阶段正式集成\n\n## Current\n\n## Next\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 22:30] 新建本轮 ACTIVE_TASK，任务切换到“双因子正式方案 + 稳健性验证”\n- [2026-04-02 22:42] 启动“双因子正式方案 + 稳健性验证”子任务，并产出正式方案文件与稳健性验证结果文件\n- [2026-04-02 22:42] 生成正式参数方案文件 dual_factor_formal_params.json\n- [2026-04-02 22:42] 生成稳健性验证结果 dual_factor_robustness_report.json/.md，确认建议进入下一阶段正式集成\n- [2026-04-02 22:42] 提交正式方案与稳健性验证，commit=05b73013e\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_overlay_backtest.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/backtest_dual_factor_overlay.py\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_formal_params.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_robustness_report.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_robustness_report.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/build_dual_factor_robustness.py\n- git commit 05b73013e 双因子稳健性验证与正式参数落地\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775141236047}}
