{"type":"message","id":"c34de0fe","parentId":"a9e9644c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:49:59.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_g6mSHB6emQqp7pzl0rJa4z9s|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce9026a6ac8196aef9ff5914a9173a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775144999059}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccc5fb0f","parentId":"c34de0fe","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:49:59.083Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YO3Kb8j5ddyKuMfiuF2KdWoP|fc_04474edf112ffe0c0169ce9026a6c08196a628bc8ad458900d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: active\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-02 23:19\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 23:19\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲确认继续推进 feature flag 灰度接线 + paper shadow wrapper\nResume Entry: 先看 ACTIVE_TASK.md，然后查看 integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py、dual_factor_integration_plan.md、dual_factor_paper_integration_readiness.json，并继续做灰度接线与纸盘 shadow 包装\n\n## Goal\n- 完成 dual factor 的 feature flag 灰度接线与 paper shadow wrapper，进入可灰度验证状态\n\n## Acceptance\n- 生成或修改正式接线代码，支持 dual factor feature flag / profile 切换\n- 生成 paper shadow wrapper 或等价接线文件，明确如何并行输出 baseline 与 dual factor 结果\n- 给出可复核结论：是否已具备进入单纸盘灰度验证条件\n\n## Current\n- 启动“feature flag 灰度接线 + paper shadow wrapper”子任务，并产出代码文件与接线结果\n\n## Next\n- 核对灰度接线与 shadow 输出口径，整理成面向张玲的验收结论\n- 提交本轮新增脚本/结果文件到 git，并回传 commit\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 23:19] 新建本轮 ACTIVE_TASK，任务切换到“feature flag 灰度接线 + paper shadow wrapper”\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_paper_integration_readiness.json\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775144999071}}
